abstract: >-
  Research repository for analyzing human preference biases in LLM outputs,
  with a focus on length preference, format preference, confounding control,
  robustness checks, matching diagnostics, and SEM-based mechanism analysis.
keywords:
  - LLM preference
  - RLHF
  - data analysis
  - robustness analysis
  - SEM
